Coda.\
\
In bucolic New Weyr, Zadane stumbles upon the entrance to a cave. Wandering in, she falls into an entrance to the underground labs beneath the town, where the mystics of Aranzen are helping their northern colleagues in a variety of experiments.  \
\
On a remote isle in the Remari Archipelago, Cereb, a winged-snake breaks open her first egg. She arises and surveys her domain.  As a huge tree erupts from the ground, threatening to blot out Fanon's light. From the egg, tens of thousands of insects and small birds dart out into the sky.\
\
Far beneath the Krunkinotto, a spy-Jax reports to Control, displaying diagrams and blueprints of flying machines. The unflappable analysts of the Created feed the new into a system that is designing what look like near-orbital trajectories. And pod are testing something like rocket fuel.  \
